descript.abstract: This coverage shows known geothermal resource areas, both existing and removed, for Idaho from the Geothermal Resources of Idaho 500K source map.
descript.purpose: This coverage is a result of the 'Geothermal Resources of Idaho' 500K map that was prepared in response to the many requests from Idahos citizens and industries for authoritative information pertaining to the states geothermal resources. Map prepared in conjunction with IDWR Water Information Bulletin No. 30, June 1980, Geothermal Investigations in Idaho (Part 9 - Potential for Direct Heat Application of Geothermal Resources).
descript.supplinf: This coverage is under review for content and locational accuracy.
